metadata.title: EMONDER Men's Long Sleeve Cycling Jersey Bike Biking Shirt Quick Dry and Breathable
features: Quick Dry:The use of high quality fabrics,softer,more elastic and frees you from the stickiness caused by sweating
Durable Technology:Elastic design with no rubber,high-stretch comfortable and unfettered,suitable for all bicycles
The Unique Non-slip Strip at the Hem: Effectively prevent clothing from swinging or even being blown by the wind during exercise,improve riding comfort
With Professional Cutting and Design:Short front and long back design greatly increase the coverage of your clothes and give you the best riding experience when you are struggling forward

The Reflective Strip and Four Pockets on the Back: One zip pocket and three back pockets,provide with plenty of space for storing everything you need.It allows you to have sufficient security at night even in environments with low visibility
description: Lightweight, breathable, fast drying, moisture-wicking jersey, mesh design for better ventilation, bring you an excellent biking experience in the summer. Four-pocket design greatly enriches storage space. Reflective strip on the back of your clothes can improve your safety while riding at night. The unique anti-slip strap at the hem effectively prevents the clothes from moving freely or even being blown by the wind during the ride.
